520718,114,1264,2,7,1,22,2,[ 527]2. Ummādantījātakavaṇṇanā 
520719,114,1265,2,13,1,96,10,Nivesanaṃ kassanudaṃ {sunandā}ti idaṃ satthā jetavane viharanto ukkaṇṭhitabhikkhuṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
520720,114,1265,14,49,1,395,34,So kirekadivasaṃ sāvatthiyaṃ piṇḍāya caranto ekaṃ alaṅkatapaṭiyattaṃ uttamarūpadharaṃ itthiṃ oloketvā paṭibaddhacitto hutvā cittaṃ nivattetuṃ asakkonto vihārameva āgantvā tato paṭṭhāya sallaviddho viya rāgāturo bhantamigapaṭibhāgo kiso dhamanīsanthatagatto uppaṇḍuppaṇḍukajāto anabhirato ekiriyāpathepi cittassādaṃ alabhanto ācariyavattādīni pahāya uddesaparipucchākammaṭṭhānānuyogarahito vihāsi. 
520721,114,1265,50,85,1,139,20,"So sahāyabhikkhūhi‘‘ pubbe tvaṃ, āvuso, santindriyo vippasannamukhavaṇṇo, idāni no tathā, kiṃ nu kho kāraṇan’’ ti puṭṭho,‘‘ āvuso, anabhiratomhī’’ ti āha. "
520722,114,1265,86,138,1,397,42,"Atha naṃ te‘‘ abhiramāvuso, sāsane, buddhuppādo nāma dullabho, tathā saddhammassavanaṃ manussapaṭilābho ca, so tvaṃ manussapaṭilābhaṃ paṭilabhitvā dukkhassantakiriyaṃ patthayamāno assumukhaṃ ñātijanaṃ pahāya saddhāya pabbajitvā kiṃkāraṇā kilesavasaṃ yāsi, kilesā nāmete gaṇḍuppādakapāṇakaṃ upādāya sabbabālajanasādhāraṇā, ye tesaṃ vatthubhūtā, tepi appassādā kāmā bahudukkhā bahupāyāsā, ādīnavo ettha bhiyyo. "
520723,114,1265,139,220,1,482,56,"Aṭṭhikaṅkalūpamā kāmā, maṃsapesūpamā kāmā, tiṇukkūpamā kāmā, aṅgārakāsūpamā kāmā, supinakūpamā kāmā, yācitakūpamā kāmā, rukkhaphalūpamā kāmā, asisūnūpamā kāmā, sattisūlūpamā kāmā, sappasirūpamā kāmā, aggikkhandhūpamā kāmā, tvaṃ nāma evarūpe buddhasāsane pabbajitvā evaṃ anatthakārakānaṃ kilesānaṃ vasaṃ gatosī’’ ti ovaditvā attano kathaṃ gāhāpetuṃ asakkontā satthu santikaṃ dhammasabhaṃ netvā‘‘ kiṃ, bhikkhave, anicchamānakaṃ bhikkhuṃ ānayitthā’’ ti vutte,‘‘ bhante, ayaṃ kira bhikkhu ukkaṇṭhito’’ ti āhaṃsu. "
520724,114,1265,221,261,1,193,27,"Satthā‘‘ saccaṃ kirā’’ ti pucchitvā‘‘ saccaṃ, bhante’’ ti vutte‘‘ bhikkhu porāṇakapaṇḍitā rajjaṃ anusāsantāpi kilese uppanne tassa vasaṃ agantvā cittaṃ nivāretvā na ayuttakaṃ kariṃsū’’ ti vatvā atītaṃ āhari. "
520725,114,1266,2,11,1,63,8,Atīte siviraṭṭhe ariṭṭhapuranagare sivi nāma rājā rajjaṃ kāresi. 
520726,114,1266,12,26,1,83,9,"Bodhisatto tassa aggamahesiyā kucchismiṃ nibbatti,‘‘ sivikumāro’’ tvevassa nāmaṃ kariṃsu. "
520727,114,1266,27,39,1,55,7,"Senāpatissapi putto jāyi,‘‘ abhipārako’’ tissa nāmaṃ kariṃsu. "
520728,114,1266,40,52,1,101,12,Te ubhopi sahāyā hutvā abhivaḍḍhantā soḷasavassikā hutvā takkasilaṃ gantvā sippaṃ uggaṇhitvā āgamiṃsu. 
520729,114,1266,53,57,1,26,4,Rājā puttassa rajjaṃ adāsi. 
520730,114,1266,58,65,1,63,7,Sopi abhipārakaṃ senāpatiṭṭhāne ṭhapetvā dhammena rajjaṃ kāresi. 
520731,114,1266,66,90,1,192,18,"Tasmiṃyeva nagare tiriṭivacchassa nāma asītikoṭivibhavassa seṭṭhino dhītā nibbatti uttamarūpadharā sobhaggappattā subhalakkhaṇena samannāgatā, tassā nāmaggahaṇadivase‘‘ ummādantī’’ ti nāmaṃ kariṃsu. "
520732,114,1266,91,103,1,130,12,Sā soḷasavassikakāle atikkantamānusavaṇṇā devaccharā viya abhirūpā dassanīyā pāsādikā paramāya vaṇṇapokkharatāya samannāgatā ahosi. 
520733,114,1266,104,126,1,160,20,"Ye ye puthujjanā taṃ passanti, te te sakabhāvena saṇṭhātuṃ asakkontā surāpānamadamattā viya kilesamadena mattā hutvā satiṃ paccupaṭṭhāpetuṃ samatthā nāma nāhesuṃ. "
520734,114,1267,2,30,1,179,21,"Athassā pitā tiriṭivaccho rājānaṃ upasaṅkamitvā‘‘ deva, mama gehe itthiratanaṃ uppannaṃ, raññova anucchavikaṃ, lakkhaṇapāṭhake brāhmaṇe pesetvā taṃ vīmaṃsāpetvā yathāruci karohī’’ ti āha. "
520735,114,1267,31,41,1,35,6,Rājā‘‘ sādhū’’ ti vatvā brāhmaṇe pesesi. 
520736,114,1267,42,48,1,62,6,Te seṭṭhigehaṃ gantvā katasakkārasammānā pāyāsaṃ paribhuñjiṃsu. 
520737,114,1267,49,56,1,69,7,Tasmiṃ khaṇe ummādantī sabbālaṅkārapaṭimaṇḍitā tesaṃ santikaṃ agamāsi. 
520738,114,1267,57,69,1,108,12,Te taṃ disvā satiṃ paccupaṭṭhāpetuṃ asakkontā kilesamadamattā hutvā attano vippakatabhojanabhāvaṃ na jāniṃsu. 
520739,114,1267,70,94,1,139,17,"Ekacce ālopaṃ gahetvā‘‘ bhuñjissāmā’’ ti saññāya sīse ṭhapesuṃ, ekacce upakacchantare khipiṃsu, ekacce bhittiṃ pahariṃsu, sabbeva ummattakā ahesuṃ. "
520740,114,1267,95,114,1,92,14,"Sā te disvā‘‘ ime kira mama lakkhaṇaṃ vīmaṃsissanti, gīvāyaṃ ne gahetvā nīharathā’’ ti nīharāpesi. "
520741,114,1267,115,136,1,112,15,"Te maṅkubhūtā rājanivesanaṃ gantvā ummādantiyā kuddhā‘‘ deva, sā itthī kāḷakaṇṇī, na tumhākaṃ anucchavikā’’ ti vadiṃsu. "
520742,114,1267,137,148,1,37,7,Rājā‘‘ kāḷakaṇṇī kirā’’ ti na taṃ āṇāpesi. 
520743,114,1267,149,188,1,175,28,"Sā taṃ pavattiṃ sutvā‘‘ ahaṃ kira kāḷakaṇṇīti raññā na gahitā, kāḷakaṇṇiyo nāma na evarūpā hontī’’ ti vatvā‘‘ hotu, sace pana taṃ rājānaṃ passissāmi, jānissāmī’’ ti tasmiṃ āghātaṃ bandhi. "
520744,114,1267,189,200,1,60,10,"Atha naṃ pitā abhipārakassa adāsi, sā tassa piyā ahosi manāpā. "
520745,114,1268,2,10,1,55,8,Kassa pana kammassa nissandena sā evaṃ abhirūpā ahosīti? 
520746,114,1268,11,13,1,31,2,Rattavatthadānassa nissandenāti. 
520747,114,1268,14,89,1,436,56,"Sā kira atīte bārāṇasiyaṃ daliddakule nibbattitvā ussavadivase puññasampannā itthiyo kusumbharattavatthaṃ nivāsetvā alaṅkatā kīḷantiyo disvā tādisaṃ vatthaṃ nivāsetvā kīḷitukāmā hutvā mātāpitūnaṃ ārocetvā tehi,‘‘ amma, mayaṃ daliddā, kuto no evarūpaṃ vatthan’’ ti vutte‘‘ tena hi maṃ ekasmiṃ aḍḍhakule bhatiṃ kātuṃ anujānātha , te mama guṇaṃ ñatvā dassantī’’ ti vatvā tehi anuññātā ekaṃ kulaṃ upasaṅkamitvā‘‘ kusumbharattavatthena bhatiṃ karomī’’ ti āha. "
520748,114,1268,90,107,1,77,13,Atha naṃ te‘‘ tīṇi saṃvaccharāni kamme kate tava guṇaṃ ñatvā dassāmā’’ ti vadiṃsu. 
520749,114,1268,108,118,1,41,6,Sā‘‘ sādhū’’ ti paṭissuṇitvā kammaṃ paṭipajji. 
520750,114,1268,119,145,1,183,22,Te tassā guṇaṃ ñatvā aparipuṇṇesuyeva tīsu saṃvaccharesu tassā ghanakusumbharattavatthena saddhiṃ aññampi vatthaṃ datvā‘‘ tava sahāyikāhi saddhiṃ gantvā nhatvā nivāsehī’’ ti taṃ pesayiṃsu. 
520751,114,1268,146,154,1,61,8,Sā sahāyikā ādāya gantvā rattavatthaṃ nadītīre ṭhapetvā nhāyi. 
520752,114,1269,2,16,1,115,14,Tasmiṃ khaṇe eko kassapadasabalassa sāvako acchinnacīvaro sākhābhaṅgaṃ nivāsetvā ca pārupitvā ca taṃ padesaṃ pāpuṇi. 
520753,114,1269,17,71,1,310,40,"Sā taṃ disvā‘‘ ayaṃ bhadanto acchinnacīvaro bhavissati, pubbepi adinnabhāvena me nivāsanaṃ dullabhaṃ jātan’’ ti taṃ vatthaṃ dvidhā phāletvā‘‘ ekaṃ koṭṭhāsaṃ ayyassa dassāmī’’ ti cintetvā uttaritvā attano nivāsanaṃ nivāsetvā‘‘ tiṭṭhatha, bhante’’ ti vatvā theraṃ vanditvā rattavatthaṃ majjhe phāletvā tassekaṃ koṭṭhāsaṃ adāsi. "
520754,114,1269,72,84,1,103,12,So ekamante paṭicchanne ṭhatvā sākhābhaṅgaṃ chaḍḍetvā tassekaṃ kaṇṇaṃ nivāsetvā ekaṃ pārupitvā nikkhami. 
520755,114,1269,85,92,1,69,7,Athassa vatthobhāsena sakalasarīraṃ taruṇasūriyo viya ekobhāsaṃ ahosi. 
520756,114,1269,93,149,1,305,43,"Sā taṃ disvā‘‘ mayhaṃ ayyo paṭhamaṃ na sobhati, idāni taruṇasūriyo viya virocati, idampi etasseva dassāmī’’ ti dutiyampi koṭṭhāsaṃ datvā‘‘ bhante, ahaṃ bhave bhave vicarantī uttamarūpadharā bhaveyyaṃ, maṃ disvā koci puriso sakabhāvena saṇṭhātuṃ mā asakkhi, mayā abhirūpatarā nāma aññā mā hotū’’ ti patthanaṃ paṭṭhapesi. "
520757,114,1269,150,154,1,32,4,Theropi anumodanaṃ katvā pakkāmi. 
520758,114,1270,2,12,1,79,10,Sā devaloke saṃsarantī tasmiṃ kāle ariṭṭhapure nibbattitvā tathā abhirūpā ahosi. 
520759,114,1270,13,22,1,80,8,"Atha tasmiṃ nagare kattikachaṇaṃ ghosayiṃsu, kattikapuṇṇamāyaṃ nagaraṃ sajjayiṃsu. "
520760,114,1270,23,65,1,255,33,"Abhipārako attano ārakkhaṭṭhānaṃ gacchanto taṃ āmantetvā‘‘ bhadde, ummādanti ajja kattikarattivāro chaṇo, rājā nagaraṃ padakkhiṇaṃ karonto paṭhamaṃ imaṃ gehadvāraṃ āgamissati, mā kho tassa attānaṃ dassesi, sopi taṃ disvā satiṃ upaṭṭhāpetuṃ na sakkhissatī’’ ti āha. "
520761,114,1270,66,96,1,131,19,"Sā‘‘ gaccha tvaṃ, sāmi, ahaṃ jānissāmī’’ ti sampaṭicchitvā tasmiṃ gate dāsiṃ āṇāpesi‘‘ rañño imaṃ gehadvāraṃ āgatakāle mayhaṃ āroceyyāsī’’ ti. "
520762,114,1270,97,123,1,258,25,Atha sūriye atthaṅgate uggahe puṇṇacande devanagare viya nagare alaṅkate sabbadisāsu dīpesu jalitesu rājā sabbālaṅkārapaṭimaṇḍito ājaññarathavaragato amaccagaṇaparivuto mahantena yasena nagaraṃ padakkhiṇaṃ karonto paṭhamameva abhipārakassa gehadvāraṃ agamāsi. 
520763,114,1270,124,131,1,94,7,Taṃ pana gehaṃ manosilāvaṇṇapākāraparikkhittaṃ alaṅkatadvāraṭṭālakaṃ sobhaggappattaṃ pāsādikaṃ. 
520764,114,1270,132,137,1,37,5,Tasmiṃ khaṇe dāsī ummādantiyā ārocesi. 
520765,114,1270,138,148,1,86,10,Sā pupphasamuggaṃ gāhāpetvā kinnarilīḷāya vātapānaṃ nissāya ṭhitā rañño pupphāni khipi. 
520766,114,1270,149,173,1,160,19,"So taṃ ulloketvā kilesamadamatto satiṃ upaṭṭhāpetuṃ asakkonto‘‘ abhipārakassetaṃ gehan’’ ti sañjānitumpi nāsakkhi, atha sārathiṃ āmantetvā pucchanto dve gāthā abhāsi– "
520767,114,1271,2,4,1,0,0,57.
520768,114,1272,2,12,1,57,8,"‘ ‘ Nivesanaṃ kassa nudaṃ sunanda, pākārena paṇḍumayena guttaṃ; "
520769,114,1273,2,10,1,55,7,"Kā dissati aggisikhāva dūre, vehāyasaṃ pabbataggeva acci. "
520770,114,1274,2,4,1,0,0,58.
520771,114,1275,2,15,1,66,11,"‘ ‘ Dhītā nvayaṃ kassa sunanda hoti, suṇisā nvayaṃ kassa athopi bhariyā; "
520772,114,1276,2,15,1,63,10,"Akkhāhi me khippamidheva puṭṭho, avāvaṭā yadi vā atthi bhattā’’ ti. "
520773,114,1277,2,9,1,35,7,Tattha kassa nudan ti kassa nu idaṃ. 
520774,114,1277,10,13,1,31,2,{Paṇḍumayenā}ti rattiṭṭhakamayena. 
520775,114,1277,14,19,1,34,4,{Dissatī}ti vātapāne ṭhitā paññāyati. 
520776,114,1277,20,23,1,24,2,{Accī}ti analajālakkhandho. 
520777,114,1277,24,31,1,29,6,Dhītā nvayan ti dhītā nu ayaṃ. 
520778,114,1277,32,36,1,32,3,{Avāvaṭā}ti apetāvaraṇā apariggahā. 
520779,114,1277,37,48,1,52,9,"{Bhattā}ti yadi vā assā sāmiko atthi, etaṃ me akkhāhīti. "
520780,114,1278,2,8,1,38,6,Athassa so ācikkhanto dve gāthā abhāsi– 
520781,114,1279,2,4,1,0,0,59.
