520786,114,1284,2,11,1,58,6,"Tassesā bhariyābhipārakassa, ummādantī nāmadheyyena rājā’’ ti. "
520787,114,1285,2,13,1,56,10,Tattha matyā ca petyā {cā}ti mātito ca pitito cetaṃ jānāmi. 
520788,114,1285,14,22,1,49,7,Athopi {assā}ti atha sāmikampi assā jānāmīti vadati. 
520789,114,1285,23,26,1,16,2,{Iddho}ti samiddho. 
520790,114,1285,27,31,1,34,3,{Phīto}ti vatthālaṅkārehi supupphito. 
520791,114,1285,32,36,1,26,3,{Suvaḍḍhito}ti suṭṭhu vuddho. 
520792,114,1285,37,40,1,21,2,{Nāmadheyyenā}ti nāmena. 
520793,114,1285,41,57,1,95,13,"Ayañhi yo naṃ passati, taṃ ummādeti, satimassa paccupaṭṭhāpetuṃ na deti, tasmā ummādantīti vuccati. "
520794,114,1286,2,10,1,53,7,Taṃ sutvā rājā nāmamassā thomento anantaraṃ gāthamāha– 
