520796,114,1288,2,15,1,60,11,"‘ ‘ Ambho ambho nāmamidaṃ imissā, matyā ca petyā ca kataṃ susādhu; "
520797,114,1289,2,13,1,57,8,"Tadā hi mayhaṃ avalokayantī, ummattakaṃ ummadantī akāsī’’ ti. "
520798,114,1290,2,12,1,46,9,Tattha matyā ca petyā {cā}ti mātarā ca pitarā ca. 
520799,114,1290,13,17,1,38,4,Mayhan ti upayogatthe sampadānavacanaṃ. 
520800,114,1290,18,29,1,83,10,{Avalokayantī}ti mayā avalokitā sayampi maṃ avalokayantī maṃ ummattakaṃ akāsīti attho. 
520801,114,1291,2,10,1,70,8,Sā tassa kampitabhāvaṃ ñatvā vātapānaṃ thaketvā sirigabbhameva agamāsi. 
520802,114,1291,11,19,1,77,8,Raññopi tassā diṭṭhakālato paṭṭhāya nagaraṃ padakkhiṇakaraṇe cittameva nāhosi. 
520803,114,1291,20,54,1,230,24,"So sārathiṃ āmantetvā,‘‘ samma sunanda, rathaṃ nivattehi, ayaṃ chaṇo amhākaṃ nānucchaviko, abhipārakassa senāpatissevānucchaviko, rajjampi tassevānucchavikan’’ ti rathaṃ nivattāpetvā pāsādaṃ abhiruyha sirisayane nipajjitvā vippalapanto āha– "
