522706,114,2282,30,73,1,209,32,"Sā ca bhājanaṃ gahetvā tattha attano ca mahāsattassa ca khujjāya ca rūpaṃ passitvā‘‘ idaṃ na aññena kataṃ, kusarājeneva katan’’ ti ñatvā kujjhitvā bhūmiyaṃ khipitvā‘‘ iminā mayhaṃ attho natthi, icchantānaṃ dehī’’ ti āha. "
522707,114,2282,74,99,1,145,18,"Athassā bhaginiyo kuddhabhāvaṃ ñatvā‘‘ khuddakabhājanaṃ kusaraññā katanti maññasi, idaṃ tena na kataṃ, kumbhakāreneva kataṃ, gaṇhāhi nan’’ ti avahasiṃsu. "
