525116,114,3735,2,7,1,25,2,[ 535]3. Sudhābhojanajātakavaṇṇanā 
525117,114,3736,2,16,1,103,13,Neva kiṇāmi napi {vikkiṇāmī}ti idaṃ satthā jetavane viharanto ekaṃ dānajjhāsayaṃ bhikkhuṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
525118,114,3736,17,40,1,257,23,So kira sāvatthiyaṃ eko kulaputto hutvā satthu dhammakathaṃ sutvā pasannacitto pabbajitvā sīlesu paripūrakārī dhutaṅgaguṇasamannāgato sabrahmacārīsu pavattamettacitto divasassa tikkhattuṃ buddhadhammasaṅghupaṭṭhāne appamatto ācārasampanno dānajjhāsayo ahosi. 
525119,114,3736,41,57,1,159,14,"Sāraṇīyadhammapūrako attanā laddhaṃ paṭiggāhakesu vijjamānesu chinnabhatto hutvāpi detiyeva, tasmā tassa dānajjhāsayadānābhiratabhāvo bhikkhusaṅghe pākaṭo ahosi. "
525120,114,3736,58,86,1,213,21,"Athekadivasaṃ bhikkhū dhammasabhāyaṃ kathaṃ samuṭṭhāpesuṃ,‘‘ āvuso, asuko nāma bhikkhu dānajjhāsayo dānābhirato attanā laddhaṃ pasatamattapānīyampi lobhaṃ chinditvā sabrahmacārīnaṃ deti, bodhisattassevassa ajjhāsayo’’ ti. "
525121,114,3736,87,172,1,484,64,"Satthā taṃ kathaṃ dibbāya sotadhātuyā sutvā gandhakuṭito nikkhamitvā āgantvā‘‘ kāya nuttha, bhikkhave, etarahi kathāya sannisinnā’’ ti pucchitvā‘‘ imāya nāmā’’ ti vutte‘‘ ayaṃ, bhikkhave, bhikkhu pubbe adānasīlo maccharī tiṇaggena telabindumpi adātā ahosi, atha naṃ ahaṃ dametvā nibbisevanaṃ katvā dānaphalaṃ vaṇṇetvā dāne patiṭṭhāpesiṃ, so‘ pasatamattaṃ udakampi labhitvā adatvā na pivissāmī’ ti mama santike varaṃ aggahesi, tassa phalena dānajjhāsayo dānābhirato jāto’’ ti vatvā tehi yācito atītaṃ āhari. "
525122,114,3737,2,12,1,86,10,Atīte bārāṇasiyaṃ brahmadatte rajjaṃ kārente eko gahapati aḍḍho ahosi asītikoṭivibhavo. 
525123,114,3737,13,18,1,32,4,Athassa rājā seṭṭhiṭṭhānaṃ adāsi . 
525124,114,3737,19,28,1,85,9,So rājapūjito nāgarajānapadapūjito hutvā ekadivasaṃ attano sampattiṃ oloketvā cintesi–
525125,114,3737,29,58,1,159,21,"‘‘ ayaṃ yaso mayā atītabhave neva niddāyantena, na kāyaduccaritādīni karontena laddho, sucaritāni pana pūretvā laddho, anāgatepi mayā mama patiṭṭhaṃ kātuṃ vaṭṭatī’’ ti. "
525126,114,3737,59,113,1,209,35,"So rañño santikaṃ gantvā‘‘ deva, mama ghare asītikoṭidhanaṃ atthi, taṃ gaṇhāhī’’ ti vatvā‘‘ na mayhaṃ tava dhanenattho, bahuṃ me dhanaṃ, itopi yadicchasi, taṃ gaṇhāhī’’ ti vutte‘‘ kiṃ nu, deva, mama dhanaṃ dātuṃ labhāmī’’ ti āha. "
525127,114,3737,114,137,1,175,19,Atha raññā‘‘ yathāruci karohī’’ ti vutte catūsu nagaradvāresu nagaramajjhe nivesanadvāre cāti cha dānasālāyo kāretvā devasikaṃ chasatasahassapariccāgaṃ karonto mahādānaṃ pavattesi. 
525128,114,3737,138,158,1,120,16,So yāvajīvaṃ dānaṃ datvā‘‘ imaṃ mama dānavaṃsaṃ mā upacchindathā’’ ti putte anusāsitvā jīvitapariyosāne sakko hutvā nibbatti. 
525129,114,3737,159,195,1,252,32,"Puttopissa tatheva dānaṃ datvā cando hutvā nibbatti, tassa putto sūriyo hutvā nibbatti, tassa putto mātali hutvā nibbatti, tassa putto pañcasikho hutvā nibbatti, tassa pana putto chaṭṭho seṭṭhiṭṭhānaṃ laddhā macchariyakosiyo nāma ahosi asītikoṭivibhavoyeva. "
525130,114,3737,196,228,1,194,25,"So‘‘ mama pitupitāmahā bālā ahesuṃ, dukkhena sambhataṃ dhanaṃ chaḍḍesuṃ, ahaṃ pana dhanaṃ rakkhissāmi, kassaci kiñci na dassāmī’’ ti cintetvā dānasālā viddhaṃsetvā agginā jhāpetvā thaddhamaccharī ahosi. "
525131,114,3738,2,26,1,144,17,"Athassa gehadvāre yācakā sannipatitvā bāhā paggayha,‘‘ mahāseṭṭhi, mā attano pitupitāmahānaṃ dānavaṃsaṃ nāsayi, dānaṃ dehī’’ ti mahāsaddena parideviṃsu. "
525132,114,3738,27,42,1,79,10,Taṃ sutvā mahājano‘‘ macchariyakosiyena attano dānavaṃso upacchinno’’ ti taṃ garahi. 
525133,114,3738,43,51,1,78,8,So lajjito nivesanadvāre yācakānaṃ āgatāgataṭṭhānaṃ nivāretuṃ ārakkhaṃ ṭhapesi. 
525134,114,3738,52,60,1,53,8,Te nippaccayā hutvā puna tassa gehadvāraṃ na olokesuṃ. 
525135,114,3738,61,89,1,247,23,"So tato paṭṭhāya dhanameva saṃharati, neva attanā paribhuñjati, na puttadārādīnaṃ deti, kañjikabilaṅgadutiyaṃ sakuṇḍakabhattaṃ bhuñjati, mūlaphalamattatantāni thūlavatthāni nivāseti, paṇṇachattaṃ matthake dhāretvā jaraggoṇayuttena jajjararathakena yāti. "
525136,114,3738,90,101,1,78,10,Iti tassa asappurisassa tattakaṃ dhanaṃ sunakhena laddhaṃ nāḷikeraṃ viya ahosi. 
525137,114,3739,2,18,1,87,11,So ekadivasaṃ rājūpaṭṭhānaṃ gacchanto‘‘ anuseṭṭhiṃ ādāya gamissāmī’’ ti tassa gehaṃ agamāsi. 
525138,114,3739,19,30,1,123,11,Tasmiṃ khaṇe anuseṭṭhi puttadhītādīhi parivuto navasappipakkamadhusakkharacuṇṇehi saṅkhataṃ pāyāsaṃ bhuñjamāno nisinno hoti. 
525139,114,3739,31,52,1,107,14,"So macchariyakosiyaṃ disvā āsanā vuṭṭhāya‘‘ ehi, mahāseṭṭhi, imasmiṃ pallaṅke nisīda, pāyāsaṃ bhuñjissāmā’’ ti āha. "
525140,114,3739,53,66,1,78,11,"Tassa pāyāsaṃ disvāva mukhe kheḷā uppajji, bhuñjitukāmo ahosi, evaṃ pana cintesi–"
525141,114,3739,67,90,1,127,16,"‘‘ sacāhaṃ bhuñjissāmi, anuseṭṭhino mama gehaṃ āgatakāle paṭisakkāro kātabbo bhavissati, evaṃ me dhanaṃ nassissati, na bhuñjissāmī’’ ti. "
525142,114,3739,91,106,1,67,10,"Atha punappunaṃ yāciyamānopi‘‘ idāni me bhuttaṃ, suhitosmī’’ ti na icchi. "
525143,114,3739,107,131,1,229,24,Anuseṭṭhimhi bhuñjante pana olokento mukhe sañjāyamānena kheḷena nisīditvā tassa bhattakiccāvasāne tena saddhiṃ rājanivesanaṃ gantvā rājānaṃ passitvā rājanivesanato otaritvā attano gehaṃ anuppatto pāyāsataṇhāya pīḷiyamāno cintesi–
525144,114,3739,132,156,1,130,15,"‘‘ sacāhaṃ‘ pāyāsaṃ bhuñjitukāmomhī’ ti vakkhāmi, mahājano bhuñjitukāmo bhavissati, bahū taṇḍulādayo nassissanti, na kassaci kathessāmī’’ ti. "
525145,114,3739,157,173,1,165,15,"So rattindivaṃ pāyāsameva cintento vītināmetvāpi dhananāsanabhayena kassaci akathetvāva pipāsaṃ adhivāsesi, anukkamena adhivāsetuṃ asakkonto uppaṇḍuppaṇḍukajāto ahosi. "
525146,114,3739,174,184,1,93,10,Evaṃ santepi dhananāsanabhayena akathento aparabhāge dubbalo hutvā sayanaṃ upagūhitvā nipajji. 
525147,114,3740,2,21,1,89,13,"Atha naṃ bhariyā upagantvā hatthena piṭṭhiṃ parimajjamānā‘‘ kiṃ te, sāmi, aphāsukan’’ ti pucchi."
525148,114,3740,22,35,1,55,8,"‘‘ Taveva sarīre aphāsukaṃ karohi, mama aphāsukaṃ natthī’’ ti."
525149,114,3740,36,68,1,134,23,"‘‘ Sāmi, uppaṇḍuppaṇḍukajātosi, kiṃ nu te kāci cintā atthi, udāhu rājā te kupito, adu puttehi avamāno kato, atha vā pana kāci taṇhā uppannā’’ ti?"
525150,114,3740,69,79,1,23,5,"‘‘ Āma, taṇhā me uppannā’’ ti."
525151,114,3740,80,88,1,15,3,"‘‘ Kathehi, sāmī’’ ti?"
525152,114,3740,89,99,1,39,5,"‘‘ Kathessāmi, sakkhissasi naṃ rakkhitun’’ ti."
525153,114,3740,100,109,1,36,4,"‘‘ Rakkhitabbayuttakā ce, rakkhissāmī’’ ti. "
525154,114,3740,110,116,1,44,5,Evampi dhananāsanabhayena kathetuṃ na ussahi. 
525155,114,3740,117,121,1,34,4,Tāya punappunaṃ pīḷiyamāno kathesi–
525156,114,3740,122,144,1,149,16,"‘‘ bhadde, ahaṃ ekadivasaṃ anuseṭṭhiṃ navasappimadhusakkharacuṇṇehi saṅkhataṃ pāyāsaṃ bhuñjantaṃ disvā tato paṭṭhāya tādisaṃ pāyāsaṃ bhuñjitukāmo jāto’’ ti."
525157,114,3740,145,160,1,80,9,"‘‘ Asappurisa, kiṃ tvaṃ duggato, sakalamārāṇasivāsīnaṃ pahonakaṃ pāyāsaṃ pacissāmī’’ ti. "
525158,114,3740,161,168,1,44,6,Athassa sīse daṇḍena paharaṇakālo viya ahosi. 
525159,114,3740,169,192,1,120,17,"So tassā kujjhitvā‘‘ jānāmahaṃ tava mahaddhanabhāvaṃ, sace te kulagharā ābhataṃ atthi, pāyāsaṃ pacitvā nāgarānaṃ dehī’’ ti āha."
525160,114,3740,193,204,1,49,7,‘‘ Tena hi ekavīthivāsīnaṃ pahonakaṃ katvā pacāmī’’ ti.
525161,114,3740,205,218,1,45,8,"‘‘ Kiṃ te etehi, attano pana santakaṃ khādantū’’ ti?"
525162,114,3740,219,233,1,68,10,‘‘ Tena hi ito cito ca sattasattagharavāsīnaṃ pahonakaṃ katvā pacāmī’’ ti.
525163,114,3740,234,242,1,15,4,‘‘ Kiṃ te etehī’’ ti.
525164,114,3740,243,253,1,35,6,‘‘ Tena hi imasmiṃ gehe parijanassā’’ ti.
525165,114,3740,254,262,1,15,4,‘‘ Kiṃ te etenā’’ ti?
525166,114,3740,263,274,1,49,7,‘‘ Tena hi bandhujanasseva pahonakaṃ katvā pacāmī’’ ti.
525167,114,3740,275,283,1,15,4,‘‘ Kiṃ te etenā’’ ti?
525168,114,3740,284,295,1,40,7,‘‘ Tena hi tuyhañca mayhañca pacāmi sāmī’’ ti.
525169,114,3740,296,307,1,30,6,"‘‘ Kāsi tvaṃ, na tuyhaṃ vaṭṭatī’’ ti?"
525170,114,3740,308,320,1,45,8,‘‘ Tena hi ekasseva te pahonakaṃ katvā pacāmī’’ ti.
525171,114,3740,321,359,1,245,31,"‘‘ Mayhañca tvaṃ mā paci, gehe pana pacante bahū paccāsīsanti, mayhaṃ pana patthaṃ taṇḍulānaṃ catubhāgaṃ khīrassa accharaṃ sakkharāya karaṇḍakaṃ sappissa karaṇḍakaṃ madhussa ekañca pacanabhājanaṃ dehi, ahaṃ araññaṃ pavisitvā tattha pacitvā bhuñjāmī’’ ti. "
525172,114,3740,360,363,1,14,3,Sā tathā akāsi. 
525173,114,3740,364,418,1,347,45,"So taṃ sabbaṃ ceṭakena gāhāpetvā‘‘ gaccha asukaṭṭhāne tiṭṭhāhī’’ ti taṃ purato pesetvā ekakova oguṇṭhikaṃ katvā aññātakavesena tattha gantvā nadītīre ekasmiṃ gacchamūle uddhanaṃ kāretvā dārudakaṃ āharāpetvā‘‘ tvaṃ gantvā ekasmiṃ magge ṭhatvā kañcideva disvā mama saññaṃ dadeyyāsi, mayā pakkositakāleva āgaccheyyāsī’’ ti taṃ pesetvā aggiṃ katvā pāyāsaṃ paci. "
525174,114,3741,2,53,1,430,39,"Tasmiṃ khaṇe sakko devarājā dasasahassayojanaṃ alaṅkatadevanagaraṃ, saṭṭhiyojanaṃ suvaṇṇavīthiṃ, yojanasahassubbedhaṃ vejayantaṃ, pañcayojanasatikaṃ sudhammasabhaṃ, saṭṭhiyojanaṃ paṇḍukambalasilāsanaṃ, pañcayojanāvaṭṭaṃ kañcanamālasetacchattaṃ, aḍḍhateyyakoṭisaṅkhā devaccharā, alaṅkatapaṭiyattaṃ attabhāvanti imaṃ attano siriṃ oloketvā‘‘ kiṃ nu kho katvā mayā ayaṃ yaso laddho’’ ti cintetvā bārāṇasiyaṃ seṭṭhibhūtena pavattitaṃ dānaṃ addasa. "
525175,114,3741,54,106,1,253,35,"Tato‘‘ mama puttādayo kuhiṃ nibbattā’’ ti olokento‘‘ putto me cando devaputto hutvā nibbatti, tassa putto sūriyo, tassa putto, mātali, tassa putto, pañcasikho’’ ti sabbesaṃ nibbattiṃ disvā‘‘ pañcasikhassa putto kīdiso’’ ti olokento attano vaṃsassa upacchinnabhāvaṃ passi. "
525176,114,3741,107,109,1,17,2,Athassa etadahosi–
525177,114,3741,110,148,1,229,29,"‘‘ ayaṃ asappuriso maccharī hutvā neva attanā paribhuñjati , na paresaṃ deti, mama vaṃso tena upacchinno, kālaṃ katvā niraye nibbattissati, ovādamassa datvā mama vaṃsaṃ patiṭṭhāpetvā etassa imasmiṃ devanagare nibbattanākāraṃ karissāmī’’ ti. "
525178,114,3741,149,209,1,390,48,"So candādayo pakkosāpetvā‘‘ etha manussapathaṃ gamissāma, macchariyakosiyena amhākaṃ vaṃso upacchinno , dānasālā jhāpitā, neva attanā paribhuñjati, na paresaṃ deti, idāni pana pāyāsaṃ bhuñjitukāmo hutvā‘ ghare paccante aññassapi pāyāso dātabbo bhavissatī’ ti araññaṃ pavisitvā ekakova pacati, etaṃ dametvā dānaphalaṃ jānāpetvā āgamissāma, apica kho pana amhehi sabbehi ekato yāciyamāno tattheva mareyya. "
525179,114,3741,210,240,1,195,23,"Mama paṭhamaṃ gantvā pāyāsaṃ yācitvā nisinnakāle tumhe brāhmaṇavaṇṇena paṭipāṭiyā āgantvā yāceyyāthā’’ ti vatvā sayaṃ tāva brāhmaṇavaṇṇena taṃ upasaṅkamitvā‘‘ bho, kataro bārāṇasigamanamaggo’’ ti pucchi. "
525180,114,3741,241,263,1,97,15,"Atha naṃ macchariyakosiyo‘‘ kiṃ ummattakosi, bārāṇasimaggampi na jānāsi, kiṃ ito esi, etto yāhī’’ ti āha. "
525181,114,3742,2,17,1,72,11,Sakko tassa vacanaṃ sutvā asuṇanto viya‘‘ kiṃ kathesī’’ ti taṃ upagacchateva. 
525182,114,3742,18,38,1,59,11,"Sopi,‘‘ are , badhira brāhmaṇa, kiṃ ito esi, purato yāhī’’ ti viravi. "
525183,114,3742,39,103,1,319,42,"Atha naṃ sakko,‘‘ bho, kasmā viravasi, dhūmo paññāyati, aggi paññāyati, pāyāso paccati, brāhmaṇānaṃ nimantanaṭṭhānena bhavitabbaṃ, ahampi brāhmaṇānaṃ bhojanakāle thokaṃ labhissāmi, kiṃ maṃ nicchubhasī’’ ti vatvā‘‘ natthettha brāhmaṇānaṃ nimantanaṃ, purato yāhī’’ ti vutte‘‘ tena hi kasmā kujjhasi, tava bhojanakāle thokaṃ labhissāmī’’ ti āha. "
525184,114,3742,104,139,1,203,28,"Atha naṃ so‘‘ ahaṃ te ekasitthampi na dassāmi, thokaṃ idaṃ mama yāpanamattameva, mayāpi cetaṃ yācitvāva laddhaṃ, tvaṃ aññato āhāraṃ pariyesāhī’’ ti vatvā bhariyaṃ yācitvā laddhabhāvaṃ sandhāyeva vatvā gāthamāha– "
525185,114,3743,2,4,1,0,0,192.
525186,114,3744,2,15,1,56,11,"‘ ‘ Neva kiṇāmi napi vikkiṇāmi, na cāpi me sannicayo ca atthi; "
525187,114,3745,2,12,1,63,7,"Sukiccharūpaṃ vatidaṃ parittaṃ, patthodano nālamayaṃ duvinnan’’ ti. "
525188,114,3746,2,34,1,147,22,"Taṃ sutvā sakko‘‘ ahampi te madhurasaddena ekaṃ silokaṃ kathessāmi, taṃ suṇāhī’’ ti vatvā‘‘ na me tava silokena attho’’ ti tassa vārentasseva gāthādvayamāha– "
525189,114,3747,2,4,1,0,0,193.
525190,114,3748,2,10,1,43,6,"‘ ‘ Appamhā appakaṃ dajjā, anumajjhato majjhakaṃ; "
525191,114,3749,2,8,1,40,5,"Bahumhā bahukaṃ dajjā, adānaṃ nūpapajjati. "
