525193,114,3751,2,13,1,43,9,"‘ ‘ Taṃ taṃ vadāmi kosiya, dehi dānāni bhuñja ca; "
525194,114,3752,2,11,1,45,6,"Ariyamaggaṃ samāruha, nekāsī labhate sukhan’’ ti. "
525195,114,3753,2,25,1,175,22,Tattha anumajjhato majjhakan ti appamattakampi majjhe chetvā dve koṭṭhāse karitvā ekaṃ koṭṭhāsaṃ datvā tato avasesato anumajjhatopi puna majjhe chetvā eko koṭṭhāso dātabboyeva. 
525196,114,3753,26,44,1,100,15,"Adānaṃ {nūpapajjatī}ti appaṃ vā bahuṃ vā dinnaṃ hotu, adānaṃ nāma na hoti, tampi dānameva mahapphalameva. "
525197,114,3754,2,26,1,98,15,"So tassa vacanaṃ sutvā‘‘ manāpaṃ te, brāhmaṇa, kathitaṃ, pāyāse pakke thokaṃ labhissasi, nisīdāhī’’ ti āha. "
525198,114,3754,27,30,1,21,3,Sakko ekamante nisīdi. 
525199,114,3754,31,43,1,110,12,Tasmiṃ nisinne cando teneva niyāmena upasaṅkamitvā tatheva kathaṃ pavattetvā tassa vārentasseva gāthādvayamāha– 
