526000,114,4151,60,79,1,172,14,"Gehe dhanadhaññādīnaṃ nāsanena coriyo, bahumāyatāya dhuttiyo, naṭṭhassatitāya asatiyo, anavaṭṭhitacittatāya lahucittāyo, katavināsanena mittadubbhitāya katassa {appaṭikārikāyo}ti. "
526001,114,4152,2,42,1,252,33,"Evañca pana vatvā‘‘ iti kho, bhikkhave, ahaṃ tiracchānagatopi itthīnaṃ akataññutaṃ bahumāyataṃ anācārataṃ dussīlatañca jānāmi, tadāpāhaṃ tāsaṃ vase avattitvā tā eva attano vase vattemī’’ ti imāya kathāya tesaṃ bhikkhūnaṃ anabhiratiṃ haritvā satthā tuṇhī ahosi. "
