526005,114,4153,2,17,1,109,9,"‘ ‘ Tasseva khalu, bho, himavato pabbatarājassa puratthimadisābhāge susukhumasunipuṇagirippabhavaharitupayantiyo’’ ti. "
526006,114,4154,2,27,1,262,20,"Tattha suṭṭhu sukhumasaṇhasalilatāya susukhumasunipuṇā, giri etāsaṃ pabhavoti girippabhavā , himavantato sandamānaharitatiṇamissaoghatāya haritā, kuṇāladahaṃ upagamanena upayantiyoti susukhumasunipuṇagirippabhavaharitupayantiyo, evarūpā nadiyo yasmiṃ sandantīti attho. "
526007,114,4155,2,12,1,62,9,"Idāni yaṃ kuṇāladahaṃ tā upayanti, tattha pupphāni vaṇṇento āha–"
526008,114,4156,2,9,1,100,4,‘ ‘ Uppalapadumakumudanalinasatapattasogandhikamandālakasampativiruḷha- suciganṭhamanuññamāvakappadese’’ ti. 
526009,114,4157,2,6,1,28,4,Tattha uppalan ti nīluppalaṃ. 
