527364,114,4627,104,157,1,219,34,"Rājā‘‘ na mayhaṃ ete manussamaṃsato piyatarā’’ ti vatvā‘‘ tena hi, mahārāja, imamhā nagarā ca raṭṭhā ca nikkhamathā’’ ti vutte,‘‘ kāḷahatthi, na me rajjenattho, nagarā nikkhamāmi, ekaṃ pana me khaggañca rasakañca bhājanañca dehī’’ ti āha. "
527365,114,4627,158,168,1,111,10,Athassa khaggañca maṃsapacanabhājanañca pacchiñca ukkhipāpetvā rasakañca datvā raṭṭhā pabbājanīyakammaṃ kariṃsu. 
527366,114,4628,2,24,1,179,21,So khaggañca rasakañca ādāya nagarā nikkhamitvā araññaṃ pavisitvā ekasmiṃ nigrodhamūle vasanaṭṭhānaṃ katvā tattha vasanto aṭavimagge ṭhatvā manusse māretvā āharitvā rasakassa deti. 
527367,114,4628,25,29,1,32,4,Sopissa maṃsaṃ pacitvā upanāmeti. 
527368,114,4628,30,33,1,19,3,Evaṃ ubhopi jīvanti. 
527369,114,4628,34,56,1,134,17,"Manussagahaṇakāle‘‘ ahaṃ are manussacoro porisādo’’ ti vatvā tasmiṃ pakkhante koci sakabhāvena saṇṭhātuṃ na sakkoti, sabbe bhūmiyaṃ patanti. "
527370,114,4628,57,69,1,72,10,"Tesu yaṃ icchati, taṃ uddhaṃpādaṃ adhosīsaṃ katvā āharitvā rasakassa deti. "
527371,114,4628,70,95,1,110,17,So ekadivasaṃ araññe kañci manussaṃ alabhitvā āgato rasakena‘‘ kiṃ devā’’ ti vutte‘‘ uddhane ukkhaliṃ āropehī’’ ti āha.
527372,114,4628,96,105,1,20,4,"‘‘ Maṃsaṃ kahaṃ, devā’’ ti?"
527373,114,4628,106,113,1,23,3,‘‘ Labhissāmahaṃ maṃsan’’ ti. 
527374,114,4628,114,130,1,75,12,So‘‘ natthi me dāni jīvitan’’ ti kampamāno uddhane aggiṃ katvā ukkhaliṃ āropesi. 
527375,114,4628,131,139,1,52,8,Atha naṃ porisādo asinā māretvā maṃsaṃ pacitvā khādi. 
527376,114,4628,140,147,1,51,7,Tato paṭṭhāya ekakova jāto sayameva pacitvā khādati.
527377,114,4628,148,160,1,68,8,‘‘ Porisādo magge maggapaṭipanne hanatī’’ ti sakalajambudīpe pākaṭo ahosi. 
527378,114,4629,2,13,1,101,11,Tadā eko sampannavibhavo brāhmaṇo pañcahi sakaṭasatehi vohāraṃ karonto pubbantato aparantaṃ sañcarati. 
527379,114,4629,14,16,1,10,2,So cintesi–
527380,114,4629,17,35,1,91,13,"‘‘ porisādo nāma kira coro antarāmagge manusse māresi, dhanaṃ datvā taṃ aṭaviṃ atikkamissāmī’’ ti. "
527381,114,4629,36,54,1,109,14,So aṭavimukhavāsīnaṃ manussānaṃ‘‘ tumhe maṃ aṭavito atikkāmethā’’ ti sahassaṃ datvā tehi saddhiṃ maggaṃ paṭipajji. 
527382,114,4629,55,72,1,180,17,Gacchanto ca brāhmaṇo sabbasatthaṃ purato katvā sayaṃ nhātānulitto sabbālaṅkārapaṭimaṇḍito setagoṇayutte sukhayānake nisinno tehi aṭavivāsikapurisehi parivuto sabbapacchato agamāsi. 
527383,114,4629,73,100,1,199,23,Tasmiṃ khaṇe porisādo rukkhaṃ āruyha purise upadhārento sesamanussesu‘‘ kiṃ imesu mayā khāditabbaṃ atthī’’ ti vigatacchando hutvā brāhmaṇaṃ diṭṭhakālato paṭṭhāya taṃ khāditukāmatāya paggharitakheḷo ahosi. 
527384,114,4629,101,129,1,160,22,So tasmiṃ attano santikaṃ āgate rukkhato oruyha‘‘ ahaṃ are porisādo’’ ti nāmaṃ tikkhattuṃ sāvetvā khaggaṃ parivattento vālukāya tesaṃ akkhīni pūrento viya pakkhandi. 
527385,114,4629,130,140,1,65,9,"Ekopi ṭhātuṃ samattho nāma natthi, sabbe bhūmiyaṃ urena nipajjiṃsu. "
527386,114,4629,141,155,1,123,14,So sukhayānake nisinnaṃ brāhmaṇaṃ pāde gahetvā piṭṭhiyaṃ adhosīsakaṃ olambetvā sīsaṃ gopphakehi paharanto ukkhipitvā pāyāsi. 
527387,114,4630,2,34,1,179,24,"Tadā te purisā uṭṭhāya,‘‘ bho, purisā mayaṃ brāhmaṇassa hatthato kahāpaṇasahassaṃ gaṇhimhā, ko nāma amhākaṃ purisakāro, sakkontā vā asakkontā vā thokaṃ anubandhāmā’’ ti vatvā anubandhiṃsu. "
527388,114,4630,35,42,1,58,7,Porisādopi nivattitvā olokento kañci aditvā saṇikaṃ pāyāsi. 
527389,114,4630,43,51,1,59,8,Tasmiṃ khaṇe thāmasampanno eko sūrapuriso vegena taṃ pāpuṇi. 
527390,114,4630,52,64,1,86,11,"So taṃ disvā ekaṃ vatiṃ laṅghanto khadirakhāṇukaṃ akkami, khāṇuko piṭṭhipādena nikkhami. "
527391,114,4630,65,69,1,38,4,Lohitena paggharantena laṅghamāno yāti. 
527392,114,4630,70,94,1,87,16,"Atha naṃ so disvā,‘‘ bho, mayā esa viddho, kevalaṃ tumhe pacchato etha, gaṇhissāmi nan’’ ti āha. "
527393,114,4630,95,100,1,39,5,Te dubbalabhāvaṃ ñatvā taṃ anubandhiṃsu. 
527394,114,4630,101,109,1,72,8,So tehi anubaddhabhāvaṃ ñatvā brāhmaṇaṃ vissajjetvā attānaṃ sotthimakāsi. 
527395,114,4630,110,125,1,94,11,Atha aṭavivāsikapurisā brāhmaṇassa laddhakālato paṭṭhāya‘‘ kiṃ amhākaṃ corenā’’ ti tato nivattiṃsu. 
527396,114,4631,2,40,1,299,30,"Porisādopi attano nigrodhamūlaṃ gantvā pārohantaraṃ pavisitvā nipanno,‘‘ ayye rukkhadevate, sace me sattāhabbhantareyeva vaṇaṃ phāsukaṃ kātuṃ sakkhissasi, sakalajambudīpe ekasatakhattiyānaṃ galalohitena tava khandhaṃ dhovitvā antehi parikkhipitvā pañcamadhuramaṃsena balikammaṃ karissāmī’’ ti āyācanaṃ kari. "
527397,114,4631,41,50,1,85,9,Tassa annapānamaṃsaṃ alabhantassa sarīraṃ sussitvā antosattāheyeva vaṇo phāsuko ahosi. 
527398,114,4631,51,56,1,50,5,So devatānubhāvena tassa phāsukabhāvaṃ sallakkhesi. 
527399,114,4631,57,64,1,57,7,So katipāhaṃ manussamaṃsaṃ khāditvā balaṃ gahetvā cintesi–
527400,114,4631,65,77,1,47,7,"‘‘ bahupakārā me devatā, āyācanā assā muccissāmī’’ ti. "
527401,114,4631,78,92,1,67,9,So khaggaṃ ādāya rukkhamūlato nikkhamitvā ‘‘ rājāno ānessāmī’’ ti pāyāsi. 
527402,114,4631,93,123,1,159,20,"Atha naṃ purimabhave yakkhakāle ekato manussamaṃsakhādako sahāyakayakkho anuvicarantaṃ disvā‘‘ ayaṃ mama atītabhave sahāyo’’ ti ñatvā,‘‘ samma, maṃ sañjānāsī’’ ti pucchi."
527403,114,4631,124,131,1,15,3,‘‘ Na sañjānāmī’’ ti. 
