529222,115,565,49,67,1,111,13,So sāsanaṃ sutvā‘‘ sādhū’’ ti sampaṭicchitvā rajjatthāya rājadvāraṃ gantvā attano āgatabhāvaṃ rājadhītāya ārocāpesi. 
529223,115,565,68,93,1,125,17,Sā tassa āgatabhāvaṃ ñatvā‘‘ atthi nu khvassa setacchattasiriṃ dhāretuṃ dhitī’’ ti tassa vīmaṃsanatthāya‘‘ khippaṃ āgacchatū’’ ti āha. 
529224,115,565,94,106,1,100,12,So tassā sāsanaṃ sutvā taṃ ārādhetukāmo sopānapādamūlato paṭṭhāya javenāgantvā tassā santike aṭṭhāsi. 
529225,115,565,107,120,1,52,9,Atha naṃ sā vīmaṃsamānā‘‘ mahātale javena dhāvā’’ ti āha. 
