529228,115,565,143,147,1,20,4,So puna vegena āgato. 
529229,115,565,148,165,1,70,12,"Sā tassa dhitiyā virahitabhāvaṃ ñatvā‘‘ ehi samma, pāde me sambāhā’’ ti āha. "
529230,115,565,166,172,1,45,6,So tassā ārādhanatthaṃ nisīditvā pāde sambāhi. 
529231,115,565,173,196,1,146,19,Atha naṃ sā ure pādena paharitvā uttānakaṃ pātetvā‘‘ imaṃ andhabālapurisaṃ dhitivirahitaṃ pothetvā gīvāyaṃ gahetvā nīharathā’’ ti dāsīnaṃ saññaṃ adāsi. 
529232,115,565,197,200,1,16,3,Tā tathā kariṃsu. 
529233,115,565,201,225,1,78,14,"So tehi‘‘ kiṃ senāpatī’’ ti puṭṭho‘‘ mā kathetha, sā neva manussitthī, yakkhinī’’ ti āha. "
