529235,115,565,234,243,1,63,7,"Tathā seṭṭhiṃ, chattaggāhaṃ, asiggāhanti sabbepi te lajjāpesiyeva. "
529236,115,566,2,27,1,157,19,"Atha amaccā sannipatitvā‘‘ rājadhītaraṃ ārādhetuṃ samattho nāma natthi, sahassathāmadhanuṃ āropetuṃ samatthassa rajjaṃ dethā’’ ti āha, tampi koci āropetuṃ nāsakkhi. "
