529241,115,566,89,112,1,138,17,"‘‘ bho tumhe mā cintayittha, phussarathaṃ nāma vissajjetuṃ vaṭṭati, phussarathena hi laddharājā sakalajambudīpe rajjaṃ kāretuṃ samattho hotī’’ ti. "
529242,115,566,113,136,1,194,19,Te‘‘ sādhū’’ ti sampaṭicchitvā nagaraṃ alaṅkārāpetvā maṅgalarathe cattāro kumudavaṇṇe asse yojetvā uttamapaccattharaṇaṃ attharitvā pañca rājakakudhabhaṇḍāni āropetvā caturaṅginiyā senāya parivāresuṃ.
529243,115,566,137,178,1,255,29,"‘‘ Sasāmikassa rathassa purato tūriyāni vajjanti, asāmikassa pacchato vajjanti, tasmā sabbatūriyāni pacchato vādethā’’ ti vatvā suvaṇṇabhiṅkārena rathadhurañca patodañca abhisiñcitvā‘‘ yassa rajjaṃ kāretuṃ puññaṃ atthi, tassa santikaṃ gacchatū’’ ti rathaṃ vissajjesuṃ. "
